long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Treer Analyze - Smart Warehouse Selection Assistant for WB

A powerful tool designed for Wildberries sellers to optimize warehouse selection. Features include:

• Real-time monitoring of warehouse storage fees
• Automatic filtering of low-cost warehouses
• Support for multiple delivery types (boxes, pallets, safebox, etc.)
• Customizable price range and date filters
• Automatic draft creation with transit warehouse selection
• Clean and intuitive interface

Save time and money by finding the most cost-effective warehouses for your business!

Treer Analyze - WB仓库智能选择助手

这是一款专为Wildberries卖家设计的智能仓库选择工具。它可以帮助您:

• 实时监控仓库入库费用变化
• 自动筛选符合条件的低价仓库
• 支持多种入库方式(普通纸箱、托盘、贵重物品、二维码等)
• 可设置想要的区间和日期范围
• 自动创建发货草稿并选择中转仓
• 界面简洁直观，使用便捷

让您轻松找到最优惠的仓库，节省入库成本！
